1
00:01:01,399 --> 00:01:03,200
The Number One Sword Under Heaven

2
00:01:05,159 --> 00:01:06,159
What are you looking at?

3
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,280
The Weapon Ranking.

4
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:09,719
What's recorded in here

5
00:01:09,719 --> 00:01:11,719
is the ranking of today's top martial artists.

6
00:01:12,439 --> 00:01:14,439
What's so interesting about that?

7
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,599
You don't get it, do you?

8
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:17,439
The Weapon Ranking is time-sensitive.

9
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:19,040
I just bought this one.

10
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:20,359
The rankings have been updated.

11
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:22,280
Wow!

12
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:25,599
Prince Huai's ranking has risen again.

13
00:01:25,599 --> 00:01:26,719
Second place!

14
00:01:27,159 --> 00:01:29,400
I really don't get you martial world types.

15
00:01:30,319 --> 00:01:31,200
Wow!

16
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:33,959
That's his third ranking jump this month!

17
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:35,560
Wow!

18
00:01:36,359 --> 00:01:38,120
Prince Chengle's thesis won another award.

19
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,640
What are you reading now?

20
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,760
Daliang Academic Journal.

21
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:42,760
Can't you read?

22
00:01:43,159 --> 00:01:44,400
You're the one who can't read!

23
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,439
Hey!

24
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:10,639
Hey!

25
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:12,800
Young hero!

26
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,520
Young hero!

27
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:19,639
Prince Huai?

28
00:02:20,759 --> 00:02:21,719
He's Prince Huai!

29
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,360
How can you tell?

30
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:27,120
Prince Huai has a truly unique scent.

31
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:31,280
I only smell chicken feet.

32
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,080
There's no fragrance at all.

33
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:32,680
That's right.

34
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:34,439
It's chicken feet, alright.

35
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,080
Ah!

36
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:37,360
Oh, heavens!

37
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,000
Such a bloody yet romantic encounter

38
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,680
has actually happened to me!

39
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:43,159
But declaring him Prince Huai just like that,

40
00:02:43,159 --> 00:02:44,800
isn't that a bit hasty?

41
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,520
Oh!

42
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:47,439
Prince Huai has a mole on his butt.

43
00:02:48,719 --> 00:02:49,879
Quick, help me check.

44
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,719
You even know that?

45
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:54,400
Of course!

46
00:02:54,599 --> 00:02:56,240
Prince Huai is my idol.

47
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,120
For my idol,

48
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:59,639
I naturally have to know everything.

49
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:00,719
Hurry up!

50
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:07,360
No way!

51
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,159
You do it yourself.

52
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:10,960
Pardon the offense!

53
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:20,879
Huh?

54
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:28,560
Who are you people?

55
00:03:28,759 --> 00:03:29,400
Huh?

56
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,719
I'm your Empress!

57
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,560
What?

58
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:33,159
Aren't you cutting straight to the chase?

59
00:03:34,039 --> 00:03:34,879
Prince Huai.

60
00:03:34,879 --> 00:03:36,560
We're special envoys from the palace.

61
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:38,039
Here to bring you back to be Emperor.

62
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:38,879
Hold on.

63
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,360
Who is Prince Huai?

64
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:41,919
Hmm.

65
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:42,680
Hmm.

66
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,800
At age six, you visited Daliang Kingdom.

67
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:46,439
To snatch the gifts your father sent,

68
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:47,960
you beat fourteen princes to tears.

69
00:03:49,039 --> 00:03:51,039
You really can see others' memories!

70
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,280
His memories have been completely erased.

71
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,159
Totally blank.

72
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,360
But the token is real.

73
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,400
He must be...

74
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,560
Prince Huai, no doubt.

75
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,400
A perfectly fine man,

76
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:05,000
how did he lose his memory?

77
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:08,639
What's this?

78
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:09,719
Oh.

79
00:04:09,719 --> 00:04:10,319
Huahua!

80
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,159
My chicken friend!

81
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:13,080
Looks pretty tasty.

82
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,560
What's tasty? What's tasty?

83
00:04:15,639 --> 00:04:16,079
Come, come, come.

84
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:16,360
Eat this.

85
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,000
Here, if you want to eat, try this.

86
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:17,439
Eat this.

87
00:04:17,439 --> 00:04:18,079
This is delicious.

88
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:18,879
This is delicious.

89
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,399
He's like this now.

90
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:22,040
How am I supposed to become Empress?

91
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,480
He never said he'd marry you anyway.

92
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,279
Hmm.

93
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:26,759
Hey!

94
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:29,439
Since he's lost his memory now,

95
00:04:29,639 --> 00:04:31,959
whatever I say goes.

96
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,759
This actually makes it easier.

97
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:38,920
My lord!

98
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,600
Do you still remember me?

99
00:04:41,079 --> 00:04:42,879
I'm your first wife of ten years!

100
00:04:42,879 --> 00:04:44,160
You said,

101
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:46,000
once you ascended the throne as Emperor,

102
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:46,879
you'd make me your Empress.

103
00:04:46,879 --> 00:04:47,759
Do you remember?

104
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,160
Hmm.

105
00:04:50,519 --> 00:04:51,920
I don't remember.

106
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:57,040
How can you forget ten years of love?

107
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:58,560
Now that the old Emperor has passed,

108
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,439
the Crown Prince refuses to take the throne,

109
00:04:59,439 --> 00:05:00,560
and the court is left without rule.

110
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:02,800
The consequences would be unimaginable!

111
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:05,240
My lord, return to Daliang and be Emperor.

112
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:05,680
Ah.

113
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,600
And by the way, crown me as Empress.

114
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,560
Sure, fine.

115
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,720
What kind of nonsense are you stirring up?

116
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,160
How old were you ten years ago?

117
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,920
He's lost his memory anyway.

118
00:05:15,959 --> 00:05:16,920
What's the big deal?

119
00:05:17,319 --> 00:05:18,279
Hey,

120
00:05:18,279 --> 00:05:20,040
I just read about this in a medical journal.

121
00:05:20,759 --> 00:05:21,560
Oh.

122
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:22,560
It's called

123
00:05:23,639 --> 00:05:25,240
shock-induced temporary amnesia.

124
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,399
He'll likely recover.

125
00:05:26,399 --> 00:05:27,319
What'll you do if he recovers?

126
00:05:27,439 --> 00:05:28,279
How will you explain?

127
00:05:28,399 --> 00:05:29,040
Recover?

128
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,279
We'll deal with it then.

129
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:32,759
His amnesia is a golden opportunity for me.

130
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,040
Besides,

131
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:36,000
amnesia won't stop him from being Emperor.

132
00:05:36,839 --> 00:05:37,560
I think

133
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,680
let's do this.

134
00:05:39,759 --> 00:05:40,759
You shock him, I'll help him.

135
00:05:40,759 --> 00:05:41,959
That way, even if he regains his memory,

136
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,600
he'll remember my kindness.

137
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,480
Fine.

138
00:05:46,879 --> 00:05:48,879
Did you prepare what I asked for?

139
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,800
Don't you trust me?

140
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:55,199
Come, Prince.

141
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,920
Relax your body.

142
00:06:00,839 --> 00:06:01,199
Imagine.

143
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:03,360
Imagine

144
00:06:06,279 --> 00:06:08,360
yourself in total darkness.

145
00:06:11,079 --> 00:06:11,680
Ouyang Yan!

146
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,759
Could you stop playing so cheerfully?

147
00:06:12,759 --> 00:06:13,800
You think this is a soccer match?

148
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:19,959
Oh.

149
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,279
Okay.

150
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,240
Come, Prince.

151
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,600
Take a deep breath.

152
00:06:30,639 --> 00:06:31,439
Yes.

153
00:06:32,959 --> 00:06:33,759
Come on.

154
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:37,879
Feel yourself in total darkness,

155
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:38,920
as if

156
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:42,240
you've entered another world.

157
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:44,600
All the noise around you

158
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:47,000
cannot disturb you.

159
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:52,000
Oh no.

160
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,079
It's not working.

161
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,959
Prince, try again.

162
00:06:56,279 --> 00:06:56,720
Come on.

163
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:57,879
Deep breath.

164
00:07:02,839 --> 00:07:03,560
Relax.

165
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:03,879
Ugh.

166
00:07:03,879 --> 00:07:04,800
No, no, no, no.

167
00:07:05,759 --> 00:07:06,759
The outside noise

168
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:08,959
is a bit too loud.

169
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,079
Ouyang Yan!

170
00:07:12,079 --> 00:07:13,199
Could you stop messing around?

171
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,800
Hey!

172
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:18,360
First you wanted melodious,

173
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,560
then you wanted passionate.

174
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,560
What do you actually want?

175
00:07:20,639 --> 00:07:22,759
With the wrong music, he can't get into the zone.

176
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,600
And you're blaming me for that?

177
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,560
Who else?

178
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:26,759
It's your lousy medical skills.

179
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:27,680
You quack!

180
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:27,920
Hey!

181
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,160
Hey.

182
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:28,800
You two,

183
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,000
I think I'm remembering something.

184
00:07:39,639 --> 00:07:40,600
Did he just say

185
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,560
he remembered?

186
00:07:48,399 --> 00:07:49,959
If it's acupuncture, fine,

187
00:07:50,279 --> 00:07:52,160
but why make me wear a doctor's robe?

188
00:07:52,279 --> 00:07:53,560
Got a problem with that?

189
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,560
Darling,

190
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,600
don't worry.

191
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:59,439
We won't hurt you.

192
00:08:00,839 --> 00:08:02,839
You just hurt me this morning.

193
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:03,720
Oh,

194
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:03,920
that...

195
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,079
that was an accident.

196
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,079
This won't hurt.

197
00:08:07,079 --> 00:08:08,000
Relax.

198
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:10,839
Push hard.

199
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,600
With all your strength.

200
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:15,040
Why is it me again?

201
00:08:15,839 --> 00:08:16,959
Didn't we agree

202
00:08:16,959 --> 00:08:18,360
you'd play the bad guy?

203
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:22,600
Darling,

204
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,839
I support you in spirit.

205
00:08:52,879 --> 00:08:53,679
Oh my!

206
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,360
You remembered something!

207
00:08:56,399 --> 00:08:57,320
Look, everyone.

208
00:09:05,679 --> 00:09:06,360
Darling.

209
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:08,240
Did you remember something?

210
00:09:10,279 --> 00:09:11,600
I remembered.

211
00:09:14,639 --> 00:09:15,879
It's been a long time

212
00:09:15,879 --> 00:09:17,679
since I last ate.

213
00:09:19,799 --> 00:09:21,159
I want chicken feet.

214
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:24,039
Chicken feet?

215
00:09:27,039 --> 00:09:29,039
This is a great opportunity!

216
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,279
Prince.

217
00:09:36,759 --> 00:09:38,360
I just heard

218
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:39,679
that you have many enemies.

219
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,399
I don't remember a single one.

220
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:47,279
Great.

221
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:49,000
This trip's gonna be a wild ride.

222
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:55,120
Look how harmless he seems.

223
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,960
How could he have offended so many

224
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:57,600
people?

225
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,279
What powerful palm strikes!

226
00:10:02,039 --> 00:10:03,360
Prince, what's wrong?

227
00:10:06,279 --> 00:10:07,559
Don't eat my chicken feet!

228
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,039
Could it be...

229
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:27,759
Prince Huai!

230
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:32,559
Hey!

231
00:10:32,559 --> 00:10:33,639
Just give up.

232
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,200
Today,

233
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:37,200
you can't escape, even with wings.

234
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,159
So it really is you,

235
00:10:40,279 --> 00:10:40,919
Prince Huai.

236
00:10:41,759 --> 00:10:42,759
Don't even think about escaping today.

237
00:10:42,759 --> 00:10:43,559
Don't move.

238
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,240
Hyah!

239
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,039
Hey, hey, hey!

240
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:54,799
Hyah!

241
00:11:04,279 --> 00:11:05,080
Hyah!

242
00:11:06,559 --> 00:11:07,360
Hyah!

243
00:11:29,639 --> 00:11:30,200
What...

244
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:32,000
is going on here?

245
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,840
I've been observing all along.

246
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,159
Though Prince Huai lost his memory,

247
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,559
his instincts remain.

248
00:11:36,639 --> 00:11:38,480
As long as he eats his beloved chicken feet,

249
00:11:38,759 --> 00:11:40,080
he gains his power.

250
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,559
And if anyone dares to take them,

251
00:11:41,679 --> 00:11:43,759
his most primal instinct kicks in:

252
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:45,639
to protect his chicken feet.

253
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:52,559
Most extreme food guarding I've ever seen.

254
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,840
Prince Huai, did you remember your martial arts?

255
00:12:27,679 --> 00:12:28,840
Someone, come quickly!

256
00:12:29,519 --> 00:12:31,399
Your Prince has returned!

257
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,759
Why is no one here?

258
00:12:55,039 --> 00:12:55,840
Prince,

259
00:12:56,759 --> 00:12:58,360
did you remember something?

260
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,120
I don't know.

261
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:06,679
I just feel like

262
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,840
this room

263
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:10,519
seems very familiar to me.

264
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:33,399
Who's there?

265
00:13:33,399 --> 00:13:35,080
Who is it?

266
00:13:35,679 --> 00:13:36,759
Stay back!

267
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:38,279
If you come closer...

268
00:13:38,279 --> 00:13:38,679
I'll...

269
00:13:38,679 --> 00:13:39,399
I'll just...

270
00:13:39,399 --> 00:13:40,399
I don't even know

271
00:13:40,519 --> 00:13:42,559
what to threaten you with!

272
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:44,799
Don't be afraid.

273
00:13:44,799 --> 00:13:46,399
We're not here to harm you.

274
00:13:46,399 --> 00:13:46,799
That's right.

275
00:13:46,799 --> 00:13:47,480
Don't be scared.

276
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:49,759
Prince Huai!

277
00:13:50,559 --> 00:13:51,360
It's Prince Huai!

278
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:53,399
Prince Huai!

279
00:13:54,799 --> 00:13:55,480
Oh.

280
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:56,399
Yes,

281
00:13:56,799 --> 00:13:57,519
I'm Prince Huai.

282
00:13:57,519 --> 00:13:59,000
Everyone's been taken!

283
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,039
Hurry and save them!

284
00:14:00,039 --> 00:14:00,840
What?

285
00:14:01,559 --> 00:14:02,519
They said,

286
00:14:02,519 --> 00:14:04,120
if you want the people from Prince Huai's manor back,

287
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:05,360
tomorrow at high noon,

288
00:14:05,559 --> 00:14:06,679
meet at the arena outside the city.

289
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:08,080
You must come alone.

290
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:08,879
Otherwise,

291
00:14:08,879 --> 00:14:10,200
just wait to collect their corpses!

292
00:14:13,279 --> 00:14:14,080
Prince Huai!

293
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:14,679
Hey.

294
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:16,559
You jianghu folk are truly vicious.

295
00:14:16,879 --> 00:14:17,679
No,

296
00:14:18,279 --> 00:14:20,759
this isn't something we jianghu folk would do.

297
00:14:23,159 --> 00:14:24,559
Then it must be...

298
00:14:26,879 --> 00:14:27,759
Liu Heng.

299
00:14:31,399 --> 00:14:32,759
I've crossed blades with Prince Huai.

300
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:34,480
His martial skill is far weaker now than before.

301
00:14:34,799 --> 00:14:35,519
Striking him at this time

302
00:14:35,519 --> 00:14:37,559
feels like taking advantage, doesn't it?

303
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:38,879
Indeed.

304
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:41,799
And using his people to force him to fight

305
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:43,759
is truly beneath our dignity.

306
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:44,759
Sigh.

307
00:14:44,759 --> 00:14:45,879
Everyone, everyone,

308
00:14:46,039 --> 00:14:47,320
you're all great heroes.

309
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:50,080
You don't want to stoop to such tactics,

310
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:51,200
and I understand that.

311
00:14:52,039 --> 00:14:53,279
But just think about it.

312
00:14:53,759 --> 00:14:55,799
All for the title of Number One Under Heaven,

313
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:58,399
he hunts down others, shattering jianghu's harmony.

314
00:14:59,399 --> 00:15:00,639
How many of our brethren

315
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:02,679
have fallen at his hands?

316
00:15:02,759 --> 00:15:04,960
Will you live your whole lives in Prince Huai's shadow,

317
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,799
forever cowering like turtles in their shells?

318
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:08,600
Don't worry, we'll definitely help you.

319
00:15:11,759 --> 00:15:12,639
Big brother!

320
00:15:13,559 --> 00:15:14,159
Big brother!

321
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:15,720
Big brother!

322
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:19,799
Big brother!

323
00:15:21,639 --> 00:15:23,200
This person smells so fragrant.

324
00:15:26,879 --> 00:15:28,799
This scent is so familiar.

325
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:30,759
Ah!

326
00:15:30,759 --> 00:15:32,080
I remember now.

327
00:15:32,279 --> 00:15:33,960
When I had an audience with the late emperor,

328
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:35,600
I smelled this same scent in the grand hall.

329
00:15:50,559 --> 00:15:51,360
Hey

330
00:15:51,759 --> 00:15:53,080
You're not dead?

331
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:55,960
Heh heh

332
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:58,120
In two hours

333
00:15:58,480 --> 00:15:59,960
the poison will take effect

334
00:16:00,159 --> 00:16:02,200
By then, your corpses will give off

335
00:16:02,799 --> 00:16:03,759
the scent of sandalwood

336
00:16:04,679 --> 00:16:05,600
Who are you?

337
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:08,000
Prince Huai

338
00:16:08,559 --> 00:16:09,639
Long time no see

339
00:16:10,279 --> 00:16:11,440
Do you still remember me?

340
00:16:13,039 --> 00:16:14,440
Of course you don't

341
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:17,120
Half of my face

342
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:18,799
ended up like this thanks to you

343
00:16:18,799 --> 00:16:19,759
I can't show my face anymore

344
00:16:20,679 --> 00:16:21,480
Today

345
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:22,879
is the day

346
00:16:22,879 --> 00:16:24,399
I get my revenge

347
00:16:25,200 --> 00:16:26,879
If you want revenge against him

348
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,879
there's a big arena just two li away

349
00:16:28,879 --> 00:16:30,759
You could fight him fair and square

350
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:32,279
Why ambush him like this?

351
00:16:32,279 --> 00:16:33,279
Hahahaha

352
00:16:34,279 --> 00:16:34,960
Hey

353
00:16:34,960 --> 00:16:36,039
Look at me

354
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:37,120
Do I look like

355
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:38,639
someone who fights fair?

356
00:16:38,639 --> 00:16:39,000
Oh

357
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:39,440
Not really

358
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:41,559
Oh my

359
00:16:41,559 --> 00:16:42,840
But speaking of dirty tricks

360
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:46,960
Prince Huai is a hundred times worse than me

361
00:16:47,759 --> 00:16:48,799
Back then

362
00:16:48,799 --> 00:16:50,559
when we were dueling on the city wall

363
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:53,000
he actually used poison against me

364
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:54,639
ruining my face completely

365
00:16:54,639 --> 00:16:56,200
Even my own mother couldn't recognize me

366
00:16:59,279 --> 00:17:00,600
So that's the kind of person I am

367
00:17:01,559 --> 00:17:02,639
I deserve to die

368
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:04,759
Kill me if you want

369
00:17:04,759 --> 00:17:05,440
Very well

370
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:06,240
Prince Huai

371
00:17:09,079 --> 00:17:09,960
This...

372
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,039
Don't let it go to waste

373
00:17:26,559 --> 00:17:27,759
Why aren't you

374
00:17:27,759 --> 00:17:29,680
killing me?

375
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:30,799
Thanks for the antidote

376
00:17:30,839 --> 00:17:31,880
May good people live in peace

377
00:17:32,440 --> 00:17:33,119
Sorry about that

378
00:17:33,119 --> 00:17:33,480
Goodbye

379
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:47,039
Come, come, come

380
00:17:47,039 --> 00:17:47,880
Everyone, come and watch

381
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:48,799
Come and watch!

382
00:17:49,119 --> 00:17:50,759
There's a duel about to start

383
00:17:51,039 --> 00:17:51,960
Come watch!

384
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:53,559
Come, come, come

385
00:17:58,640 --> 00:17:59,880
The duel is starting!

386
00:18:25,880 --> 00:18:26,359
Why are you dodging?

387
00:18:26,559 --> 00:18:27,480
Fight back!

388
00:18:33,279 --> 00:18:34,000
What do we do?

389
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:35,160
Prince Huai is no match for him

390
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:38,720
Fight!

391
00:18:39,039 --> 00:18:42,559
Get up!

392
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:47,559
Get up!

393
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:50,480
Keep fighting!

394
00:18:51,279 --> 00:18:52,440
Keep going!

395
00:19:16,799 --> 00:19:17,359
Alright

396
00:19:17,519 --> 00:19:18,680
End of round one

397
00:19:18,839 --> 00:19:20,480
Prince Huai wins

398
00:19:35,359 --> 00:19:36,119
Well fought!

399
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:40,480
Ah

400
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:41,839
Without chicken feet

401
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:43,200
he's lost all his powers

402
00:19:43,799 --> 00:19:45,240
He can't fight the next round

403
00:19:46,119 --> 00:19:46,960
What should we do?

404
00:19:47,559 --> 00:19:48,240
Here's the plan

405
00:19:48,240 --> 00:19:49,599
You two, stall for as long as you can

406
00:19:49,680 --> 00:19:51,400
I'll see if anyone nearby is selling some

407
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:53,960
Boss

408
00:19:53,960 --> 00:19:55,200
Wrap them all up for me

409
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:56,000
Hey

410
00:19:56,480 --> 00:19:57,279
Hold them tight

411
00:19:58,680 --> 00:19:59,400
Boss

412
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:00,359
Got any more chicken feet?

413
00:20:00,599 --> 00:20:01,759
You're a step too late

414
00:20:01,839 --> 00:20:03,759
This gentleman just bought them all

415
00:20:05,559 --> 00:20:07,160
Liu Heng, why buy so many chicken feet?

416
00:20:08,359 --> 00:20:09,599
Why are you everywhere?

417
00:20:11,039 --> 00:20:11,559
Hey

418
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:13,839
Listen, you bookworm

419
00:20:13,839 --> 00:20:15,079
Don't overestimate yourself

420
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:16,279
Without Ouyang Yan

421
00:20:16,880 --> 00:20:18,319
you're nothing but a weakling

422
00:20:19,079 --> 00:20:20,440
Liu Heng, you're so despicable!

423
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:45,519
Now this'll be a good show

424
00:20:45,519 --> 00:20:46,759
This newcomer is quite formidable

425
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:57,039
Prince Huai

426
00:20:57,039 --> 00:20:58,920
Just give up

427
00:20:59,359 --> 00:21:01,000
You can't beat me

428
00:21:01,759 --> 00:21:02,720
Who are you?

429
00:21:07,680 --> 00:21:09,200
I think I've seen you before

430
00:21:14,400 --> 00:21:15,240
Enough talk

431
00:21:15,240 --> 00:21:16,880
Take this!

432
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:19,680
Today, either you die

433
00:21:20,599 --> 00:21:21,839
or I perish

434
00:21:48,559 --> 00:21:50,079
Why aren't you fighting back?

435
00:21:53,759 --> 00:21:55,559
So what if I love chicken feet?

436
00:21:56,559 --> 00:21:57,359
Bookworm

437
00:21:57,680 --> 00:22:00,000
You really think Prince Huai is a good guy?

438
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:02,160
Let me tell you this

439
00:22:02,359 --> 00:22:04,440
If my Royal Brother became Emperor

440
00:22:04,680 --> 00:22:05,599
He'd probably

441
00:22:06,079 --> 00:22:08,000
be ten thousand times more vile than me

442
00:22:08,079 --> 00:22:08,880
You...

443
00:22:08,880 --> 00:22:09,920
You what?

444
00:22:10,279 --> 00:22:11,960
You still have time to waste here with me?

445
00:22:12,880 --> 00:22:14,839
If you head back any later

446
00:22:15,359 --> 00:22:16,799
I'm afraid my Royal Brother

447
00:22:16,799 --> 00:22:18,720
will be beaten to death

448
00:22:20,960 --> 00:22:21,799
Go!

449
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:23,519
Hey

450
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:29,640
I've forgotten all my martial arts

451
00:22:31,440 --> 00:22:32,359
Forgotten?

452
00:22:33,240 --> 00:22:33,759
Hmph

453
00:22:33,759 --> 00:22:35,160
What karma

454
00:22:36,319 --> 00:22:38,200
You shattered the One-Armed Hero's arm

455
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:40,240
chopped off Shadowless Kick's foot

456
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:42,640
sliced off Single Yang Finger's finger

457
00:22:43,279 --> 00:22:44,720
Don't tell me you've forgotten that too

458
00:22:46,119 --> 00:22:47,440
I did all those things?

459
00:22:52,759 --> 00:22:53,279
Hey!

460
00:22:53,279 --> 00:22:54,559
You can't just cheat!

461
00:22:55,720 --> 00:22:56,519
Darling

462
00:22:57,200 --> 00:22:58,000
Who are you?

463
00:22:59,960 --> 00:23:01,279
I'm Prince Huai's princess consort

464
00:23:01,640 --> 00:23:03,640
And the future Empress of Daliang

465
00:23:05,160 --> 00:23:06,200
You step aside

466
00:23:06,519 --> 00:23:07,559
I don't hit women

467
00:23:08,759 --> 00:23:09,559
That's all right

468
00:23:10,599 --> 00:23:12,000
I hit men

469
00:23:45,039 --> 00:23:47,240
Hurry!

470
00:23:58,440 --> 00:23:59,240
Darling!

471
00:24:07,720 --> 00:24:08,519
Darling!

472
00:24:08,839 --> 00:24:09,640
Are you all right?

473
00:24:10,599 --> 00:24:11,400
Ah

474
00:24:25,160 --> 00:24:25,960
It's you

475
00:24:28,960 --> 00:24:29,680
Darling

476
00:24:29,680 --> 00:24:30,880
You remember now?

477
00:24:32,319 --> 00:24:33,119
Darling

478
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:37,039
Yes, yes, yes

479
00:24:38,079 --> 00:24:40,359
While you had amnesia, we

480
00:24:40,359 --> 00:24:40,880
got married

481
00:24:43,599 --> 00:24:45,119
That's incredibly shameless of you!

482
00:24:46,319 --> 00:24:47,480
Cut the nonsense

483
00:24:47,519 --> 00:24:48,359
Are we fighting or not?

484
00:24:50,960 --> 00:24:51,759
Fight

485
00:24:54,359 --> 00:24:55,240
Of course we fight

486
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:57,799
Wait a moment

487
00:24:58,200 --> 00:24:59,000
Mm

488
00:26:04,720 --> 00:26:06,039
You're Number One Under Heaven now

489
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:07,720
What's so great about being Number One?

490
00:26:09,960 --> 00:26:10,759
It's boring

491
00:26:26,039 --> 00:26:28,240
Thank you both for your help all this time

492
00:26:28,559 --> 00:26:29,359
No need for thanks

493
00:26:30,279 --> 00:26:31,079
Darling

494
00:26:31,759 --> 00:26:33,319
Let's go back so you can be Emperor

495
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:36,440
Heh heh

496
00:26:39,680 --> 00:26:41,559
A beauty like you wanting to marry me

497
00:26:41,759 --> 00:26:43,079
This prince couldn't ask for more

498
00:26:44,759 --> 00:26:45,599
But I know

499
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:47,319
we never actually got married

500
00:26:47,440 --> 00:26:48,920
And I can't go back to be Emperor

501
00:26:49,279 --> 00:26:49,720
You...

502
00:26:50,039 --> 00:26:52,039
How can you break your word like this?

503
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:54,960
Because in the past

504
00:26:54,960 --> 00:26:57,119
to climb the Weapon Ranking

505
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:58,440
I was too ruthless

506
00:26:58,440 --> 00:26:59,799
and crippled too many people

507
00:27:01,240 --> 00:27:02,960
They can't take care of themselves now

508
00:27:03,759 --> 00:27:05,000
So I've decided

509
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:06,160
to take responsibility for them

510
00:27:06,440 --> 00:27:07,799
and open a retirement home for warriors

511
00:27:08,079 --> 00:27:09,400
so they can live out their golden years

512
00:27:10,279 --> 00:27:11,359
Please follow me

513
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:41,279
They've completely lost their martial powers

514
00:27:45,279 --> 00:27:46,839
If their enemies come for them

515
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:48,559
they'll surely die without a chance

516
00:27:48,599 --> 00:27:49,119
So

517
00:27:49,119 --> 00:27:50,720
I must stay here and protect them

518
00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:53,880
and care for each of them

519
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:55,680
until they pass on

520
00:28:06,240 --> 00:28:07,799
The martial world fights over hollow fame

521
00:28:08,799 --> 00:28:10,680
yet causes so much strife and slaughter

522
00:28:14,519 --> 00:28:15,880
Let alone being the Emperor
